  <entry>
    <title>Paimon-[卷I]-核心概念</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/24/paimon-230718/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/24/paimon-230718/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>  /* 设置整个页面的字体 */  html, body, .markdown-body {    font-family: STXihei, "华文细黑", "Microsoft YaHei", "微软雅黑";    font-size: 15px;  }</style><h2 id="01-总览"><a href="#01-总览" class="headerlink" title="01 总览"></a>01 总览</h2><p><strong>Streaming data lake platform with high-speed data ingestion, changelog tracking and efficient real-time analytics.</strong></p><p>Paimon 是一个具有 <code>高速数据摄取</code>、<code>变更日志跟踪</code> 和 <code>高效实时分析</code> 功能的 <strong>流数据湖平台</strong></p><p><a href="https://paimon.apache.org/">官网</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/docs/master">文档</a>、<a href="https://github.com/apache/incubator-paimon/">GitHub</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/community/how-to-contribute/">贡献指南</a>、<a href="https://paimon.apache.org/docs/master/project/roadmap/">Roadmap</a></p><div class="note note-info">            <p>Paimon核心支持Flink的数据读取，同时也支持Hive、Spark、Trino等计算引擎的读取</p>          </div><h3 id="1-1-架构"><a href="#1-1-架构" class="headerlink" title="1.1 架构"></a>1.1 架构</h3><p><img src="/img/paimon-architecture.png" alt="Paimon Architecture"></p><h3 id="1-2-基本概念-Basic-Concepts"><a href="#1-2-基本概念-Basic-Concepts" class="headerlink" title="1.2 基本概念 Basic Concepts"></a>1.2 基本概念 Basic Concepts</h3><ul><li><strong>Snapshot</strong><sup>快照</sup>: 快照是对表再某一瞬间的 <code>状态记录</code>，因此可以让用户进行Time-traveling(时间旅行)；</li><li><strong>Partition</strong><sup>分区</sup>: 和Hive类似，Paimon将数据按照分区来切分数据块；<br><span class="label label-primary">如果定义了主键，分区键必须是主键的子集。</span></li><li><strong>Bucket</strong><sup>桶</sup>: 对于 非分区表、已分区表 进行 <code>二次数据切分</code>。用户可以通过提供 <code>bucket-key</code> 选项来指定bucket列<br><span class="label label-primary">Bucket 是针对 <code>读/写的最小存储单元</code>，因此bucket的数量限制了最大的处理并行性。但是，这个数字不应该太大，因为它将导致大量小文件和低读取性能。<u>一般情况下，建议每个bucket中的数据大小为<strong>1GB</strong>左右</u></span></li><li><strong>Consistency Guarantees</strong><sup>一致性保证</sup>: 写表时，Paimon通过 <code>两阶段提交协议</code> 自动将一批记录提交出去（每次提交时最多产生两次snapshot）</li></ul><h2 id="02-核心"><a href="#02-核心" class="headerlink" title="02 核心"></a>02 核心</h2><h3 id="1-3-文件布局"><a href="#1-3-文件布局" class="headerlink" title="1.3 文件布局"></a>1.3 文件布局</h3><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-layout.png" alt="Paimon File Layout"></p><ol><li><strong>Snapshot Files</strong><sup>快照文件</sup>: 快照文件均存储在上图的 <code>snapshot</code> 文件夹中，这些文件是 JSON 格式的，其中包含了 <span class="label label-info">元数据信息</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">快照的变更记录列表</span></li><li><strong>Manifest Files</strong><sup>清单文件</sup>: 清单文件均存储在上图的 <code>manifest</code> 文件夹中， 每个 <code>manifest-list</code> 中由1个以上的 <code>manifest-file</code> 组成，每个 manifset-file 包含了 <span class="label label-info">LSM数据文件</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">changelog files</span></li><li><strong>Data Files</strong><sup>数据文件</sup>: 数据文件由 <code>partitions</code> 和 <code>buckets</code> 所组织，每个桶目录包含了一个 <span class="label label-info">LSM tree</span> 以及它的 <span class="label label-info">changelog files</span></li></ol><h4 id="1-3-1-简述-LSM-Trees"><a href="#1-3-1-简述-LSM-Trees" class="headerlink" title="1.3.1 简述 LSM-Trees"></a>1.3.1 简述 LSM-Trees</h4><p><img src="/img/lsm-sorted-run.png" alt="LSM"></p><p>LSM 树将文件以多个 <span class="label label-success">sorted runs</span><sup>序运行</sup> 组成。<code>sorted runs</code> 由多个 <code>data files</code> 组成，每个<code>sorted runs</code> 都是唯一的。</p><h5 id="查询操作"><a href="#查询操作" class="headerlink" title="查询操作"></a>查询操作</h5><p>不同的 <code>sorted runs</code> 中可能包含相同主键的 <code>data files</code>，所以 <span class="label label-danger">在查询LSM树的时候，必须按照用户指定的合并引擎规则搭配时间戳合并相同主键的sorted runs集合</span></p><h5 id="写入操作"><a href="#写入操作" class="headerlink" title="写入操作"></a>写入操作</h5><p>新纪录将首先在内存中缓冲，当缓冲区已满时，将对内存中的所有记录进行排序并刷写到磁盘中。</p><h5 id="合并操作"><a href="#合并操作" class="headerlink" title="合并操作"></a>合并操作</h5><p>当越来越多的数据写入LSM树，刷写出来的 <code>sorted runs</code> 将会堆积，为了处理因为大量 <code>sorted runs</code> 带来的查询性能低下(甚至是OOM情形)，Paimon使用了 <span class="label label-info">Compaction</span> 操作来合并小单位的 <code>sorted runs</code>。</p><p>类似于 Rocksdb 的 <em>universal compation</em>[^1]，Paimon 的Compaction策略也是在”读”&#x2F;“写”之间进行性能的抉择，因为合并动作对于数据块来说是一个敏感的锁式操作，对于CPU和磁盘I&#x2F;O影响较大。</p><h3 id="1-4-文件操作"><a href="#1-4-文件操作" class="headerlink" title="1.4 文件操作"></a>1.4 文件操作</h3><h4 id="1-4-1-Flink集成Paimon"><a href="#1-4-1-Flink集成Paimon" class="headerlink" title="1.4.1 Flink集成Paimon"></a>1.4.1 Flink集成Paimon</h4><p>从 <a href="https://repository.apache.org/snapshots/org/apache/paimon/">Flink集成jar包</a> 路径下载对应flink版本的官方jar包(1.14&#x2F;1.15&#x2F;1.16&#x2F;1.17)，拷贝到 <code>$FLINK_HOME/lib/</code> 下(按需改名)</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>此处编者使用了 <code>paimon-flink-1.17-0.5.jar</code> 作为三方包</p>          </div><p>如果是 <em>flink on hadoop</em> 集成环境，还需进行如下操作之一：</p><ul><li>环境变量注入 <code>$HADOOP_CLASSPATH</code> <span class="label label-info">编者配置了但不使用HDFS等分布式存储</span></li><li>引入三方shaded包(flink-shaded-hadoop-2-uber-*.jar)至 <code>$FLINK_HOME/lib/</code> 中</li></ul><p>修改flink的TM工作槽为2，从而方便后续的 <em>多任务功能</em> 校验</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">taskmanager.numberOfTaskSlots:</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过 sql-client.sh 进行简单的 FlinkSQL 操作 Paimon 表验证：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sh <span class="hljs-variable">$FLINK_HOME</span>/bin/sql-client.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-warning">            <p>使用 sql-client 时建议执行 <code>SET execution.runtime-mode=BATCH;</code> ，将整体模式设置为批处理；避免遇上删除等不兼容流处理的问题。</p>          </div><h4 id="1-4-2-操作速览"><a href="#1-4-2-操作速览" class="headerlink" title="1.4.2 操作速览"></a>1.4.2 操作速览</h4><h5 id="创建Catalog"><a href="#创建Catalog" class="headerlink" title="创建Catalog"></a>创建Catalog</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-comment">-- warehouse的路径在分布式路径中使用专有协议，如 HDFS 或 OSS 等</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> CATALOG my_catalog <span class="hljs-keyword">WITH</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;type&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;paimon&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;warehouse&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;file:/tmp/paimon&#x27;</span><br>);<br><br>USE CATALOG my_catalog;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="创建表"><a href="#创建表" class="headerlink" title="创建表"></a>创建表</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> T (<br>  id <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span>,<br>  a <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>  b STRING,<br>  dt STRING COMMENT <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;timestamp string in format yyyyMMdd&#x27;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY(id, dt) <span class="hljs-keyword">NOT</span> ENFORCED<br>) PARTITIONED <span class="hljs-keyword">BY</span> (dt);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>操作以后可以本地查看到表结构：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">pwd</span><br>/tmp/paimon<br>tree<br>.<br>└── default.db<br>    └── T<br>        └── schema<br>            └── schema-0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="插入单条数据"><a href="#插入单条数据" class="headerlink" title="插入单条数据"></a>插入单条数据</h5><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10001</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00001&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230501&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时可以进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">tree<br>.<br>├── dt=20230501<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-464db983-ff5e-47cc-9fcc-2ec7d7c89d37-0.orc<br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    └── snapshot-1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-0.png" alt="首次快照插入流程"></p><p>接下来我们逐一分析 <span class="label label-danger">重点文件</span>：</p><h6 id="snapshot-1"><a href="#snapshot-1" class="headerlink" title="snapshot-1"></a>snapshot-1</h6><p>包含了快照的 <em>元数据信息</em></p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;version&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;id&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;schemaId&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;baseManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;deltaManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;changelogManifestList&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-literal"><span class="hljs-keyword">null</span></span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitUser&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;32d30dbe-ef3d-46ba-959b-267917cb538d&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitIdentifier&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">9223372036854775807</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;commitKind&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;APPEND&quot;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;timeMillis&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1690157348811</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;logOffsets&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;totalRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;deltaRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;changelogRecordCount&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">&quot;watermark&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span> <span class="hljs-number">-9223372036854775808</span><br><span class="hljs-punctuation">&#125;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>它描述了两个核心概念：<span class="label label-info">baseManifestList</span> 和 <span class="label label-info">deltaManifestList</span>；</p><ul><li><strong>baseManifestList</strong>：基础清单列表，有关deltaManifestList的每次更改都将应用于baseManifestList；<blockquote><p>对应到上面的流程图中就是 <em>manifest-list-1-base</em></p></blockquote></li><li><strong>deltaManifestList</strong>：每次操作的增量清单列表。（附属 <code>manifest file</code> 的生成）<blockquote><p>对应到上面的流程图中就是 <em>manifest-list-1-delta</em> 和 <em>manifest-1-0</em></p></blockquote></li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>首次提交会产生1个 <code>manifest file</code> 和2个 <code>manifest lists</code></p>          </div><h6 id="manifest-manifest-list"><a href="#manifest-manifest-list" class="headerlink" title="manifest &amp; manifest-list"></a>manifest &amp; manifest-list</h6><p>看完核心概念再来看编者 <code>manifest</code>文件夹下 的实际文件：</p><ul><li>manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0：存储并描述了数据文件块在快照中信息；</li><li>manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0：实际上是空的</li><li>manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1：包含了对数据文件执行操作的清单条目列表</li></ul><h5 id="插入批量数据"><a href="#插入批量数据" class="headerlink" title="插入批量数据"></a>插入批量数据</h5><p>FlinkSQL执行：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> <br>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10002</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00002&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230502&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10003</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00003&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230503&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">4</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10004</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00004&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230504&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10005</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00005&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230505&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">6</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10006</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00006&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230506&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">7</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10007</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00007&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230507&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">8</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10008</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00008&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230508&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">9</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10009</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00009&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230509&#x27;</span>),<br>(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10010</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;varchar00010&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230510&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">tree<br>.<br>├── dt=20230501<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-464db983-ff5e-47cc-9fcc-2ec7d7c89d37-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230502<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-cc196bd5-f86c-426f-a6af-eff0d5d394f5-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230503<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-0dbb8fab-01cb-43fa-bd37-fa9c9d96ceff-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230504<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-e6973ba6-c00f-42ed-8369-60889f8c0ba2-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230505<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-8242dd5d-33cd-46a7-97e3-99a3968d6ed1-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230506<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-d7ff1a46-02e8-4713-a53d-89b357c6a5bb-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230507<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-dadac0a6-5503-494e-8fdc-c9d7dcfee79a-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230508<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-8e123e3c-90e8-49e4-9d08-6c222e41ba0d-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230509<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-ac3be585-7b8a-4b3e-b756-738f69d0ad0b-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230510<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-835009a9-863a-4301-bce3-d94ec7ba13b0-0.orc<br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-2526d0f2-81ff-429b-af9a-8707d050c17c-0<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    ├── snapshot-1<br>    └── snapshot-2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-1.png" alt="二次(批量)快照插入流程"></p><p>可以看到，第一次快照动作产生的 <code>baseManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-base) 和 <code>deltaManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-delta) 已经不再被最新的快照 <code>snapshot-2</code> 所描述，新产生的 <code>baseManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-base) 是合并了 <code>snapshot-1</code> 中增量清单列表和基础清单列表的结果（manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-base &#x3D;&gt; manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-base + manifest-list-<strong>1</strong>-delta）</p><p>同时由 <code>snapshot-2</code> 产生的 <code>deltaManifestList</code>(manifest-list-<strong>2</strong>-delta) 将用于描述本次批量插入的从 20230502分区 ~ 20230510分区 的数据增量信息。</p><div class="note note-info">            <p>不难猜出，对于某张表每次的快照插入操作，都会将上一次的 <code>deltaManifestList</code> 和 <code>baseManifestList</code> 按照某种合并策略进行 <strong>Compaction</strong></p>          </div><h5 id="删除数据"><a href="#删除数据" class="headerlink" title="删除数据"></a>删除数据</h5><p>接下来，我们执行 <code>snapshot-3</code> 删除操作：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">DELETE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">WHERE</span> dt<span class="hljs-operator">&gt;=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;20230503&#x27;</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">tree<br>.<br>├── dt=20230501<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-464db983-ff5e-47cc-9fcc-2ec7d7c89d37-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230502<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       └── data-cc196bd5-f86c-426f-a6af-eff0d5d394f5-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230503<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-0dbb8fab-01cb-43fa-bd37-fa9c9d96ceff-0.orc<br>│       └── data-753409df-f434-455d-8187-9cd645328c01-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230504<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-04d1fd0c-b3d2-4b3a-a722-fc8e1ca602f0-0.orc<br>│       └── data-e6973ba6-c00f-42ed-8369-60889f8c0ba2-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230505<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-8242dd5d-33cd-46a7-97e3-99a3968d6ed1-0.orc<br>│       └── data-bf56e6e7-8269-4c61-b221-3edcc4019336-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230506<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-d7ff1a46-02e8-4713-a53d-89b357c6a5bb-0.orc<br>│       └── data-fa78c26d-9e8b-4169-a224-b192cf0ac7d7-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230507<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-a6787745-5bfc-4318-b208-21ff46eafa43-0.orc<br>│       └── data-dadac0a6-5503-494e-8fdc-c9d7dcfee79a-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230508<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-3411d3a5-6c0a-4010-a341-c828c4c85bf9-0.orc<br>│       └── data-8e123e3c-90e8-49e4-9d08-6c222e41ba0d-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230509<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-6e106fae-4642-42a5-a49d-b190e94eb4c1-0.orc<br>│       └── data-ac3be585-7b8a-4b3e-b756-738f69d0ad0b-0.orc<br>├── dt=20230510<br>│   └── bucket-0<br>│       ├── data-3e1c8cf6-bfee-40d9-ac0e-cb9a454071da-0.orc<br>│       └── data-835009a9-863a-4301-bce3-d94ec7ba13b0-0.orc<br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-2526d0f2-81ff-429b-af9a-8707d050c17c-0<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-d002ed10-727b-4422-b519-fc43b80ce770-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-38656eed-018f-4b52-a465-18382c60ad82-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-38656eed-018f-4b52-a465-18382c60ad82-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    ├── snapshot-1<br>    ├── snapshot-2<br>    └── snapshot-3<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看出，<strong>没有任何的分区会真正被删除</strong>，而是在相关分区中加入了新的 .orc 数据文件，例如分区dt&#x3D;20230510：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">./T/dt=20230510/bucket-0:<br>data-3e1c8cf6-bfee-40d9-ac0e-cb9a454071da-0.orc <span class="hljs-comment"># 由 delete操作 产生的新数据</span><br>data-835009a9-863a-4301-bce3-d94ec7ba13b0-0.orc <span class="hljs-comment"># 由 insert操作 产生的旧数据</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>具体流程对应到下图：</p><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-2.png" alt="删除操作流程"></p><div class="note note-waring">            <p>需特别注意，<code>manifest-3-0</code> 实际上还包含了原本被“删除”的8个分区的新增清单条目（紫色的<code>data-insert-0</code>）</p>          </div><p>当我们执行查询语句的时候，显示如下：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> T;<br><span class="hljs-comment">--------------------------------------------</span><br>id      <span class="hljs-operator">|</span>a        <span class="hljs-operator">|</span>b               <span class="hljs-operator">|</span>dt<br><span class="hljs-number">1</span>       <span class="hljs-operator">|</span><span class="hljs-number">10001</span>    <span class="hljs-operator">|</span>varchar00001    <span class="hljs-operator">|</span><span class="hljs-number">20230501</span><br><span class="hljs-number">2</span>       <span class="hljs-operator">|</span><span class="hljs-number">10002</span>    <span class="hljs-operator">|</span>varchar00002    <span class="hljs-operator">|</span><span class="hljs-number">20230502</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="压缩数据"><a href="#压缩数据" class="headerlink" title="压缩数据"></a>压缩数据</h5><p>随着小文件的增加，会导致后续的读性能下降，因此压缩的触发很有必要</p><div class="note note-warning">            <p>主动执行合并操作需要下载 <code>paimon-flink-action-xxx.jar</code> 包，可以理解为一个Flink引擎下的分离工具包</p>          </div><p>合并指令模板：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;FLINK_HOME&#125;</span><br>./bin/flink run /path/to/paimon-flink-action-0.5-SNAPSHOT.jar \<br>    compact \<br>    --warehouse &lt;warehouse-path&gt; \<br>    --database &lt;database-name&gt; \ <br>    --table &lt;table-name&gt; \<br>    [--partition &lt;partition-name&gt;] \<br>    [--catalog-conf &lt;paimon-catalog-conf&gt; [--catalog-conf &lt;paimon-catalog-conf&gt; ...]] \<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>衔接上一节的实际操作命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;FLINK_HOME&#125;</span><br>./bin/flink run \<br>    -Dexecution.runtime-mode=BATCH \<br>    ./lib/paimon-flink-action-0.5-SNAPSHOT.jar \<br>    compact \<br>    --path file:///tmp/paimon/default.db/T<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-warning">            <p>编者使用的是 flink-1.17，默认运行时使用 stream 模式，所以按照官方案例操作会导致任务迟迟加载不到数据。在此使用 <code>-Dexecution.runtime-mode=BATCH</code> 指定任务为批模式。</p>          </div><p>进入 <code>/tmp/paimon/default.db/T/</code> 查看文件层次：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">tree<br>.<br>├── ...(No Changes)<br>│   <br>├── manifest<br>│   ├── manifest-2526d0f2-81ff-429b-af9a-8707d050c17c-0<br>│   ├── manifest-bf837539-b6ae-4dc3-8733-325e469cb17d-0<br>│   ├── manifest-d002ed10-727b-4422-b519-fc43b80ce770-0<br>│   ├── manifest-f14fd694-3520-4f5d-8ee7-67921b5f30af-0 <span class="hljs-comment"># 新增</span><br>│   ├── manifest-list-38656eed-018f-4b52-a465-18382c60ad82-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-38656eed-018f-4b52-a465-18382c60ad82-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-0<br>│   ├── manifest-list-895bb140-b495-4383-90c4-bde76f39ea50-1<br>│   ├── manifest-list-9d509042-5dd6-4043-bd35-09a6ec378dfe-0 <span class="hljs-comment"># 新增</span><br>│   ├── manifest-list-9d509042-5dd6-4043-bd35-09a6ec378dfe-1 <span class="hljs-comment"># 新增</span><br>│   ├── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-0<br>│   └── manifest-list-ddd3d3c8-a97c-4637-bd43-dd1cec139c62-1<br>├── schema<br>│   └── schema-0<br>└── snapshot<br>    ├── EARLIEST<br>    ├── LATEST<br>    ├── snapshot-1<br>    ├── snapshot-2<br>    ├── snapshot-3<br>    └── snapshot-4<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新的流程如下图：</p><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-3.png" alt="合并操作流程"></p><div class="note note-warning">            <p>需特别注意，<code>manifest-4-0</code> 实际上包含了20个清单条目（18个删除操作清单 + 2个新增操作清单）</p><ul><li>18个删除清单：<ul><li>分区 20230503 to 20230510，每个分区有2个删除操作，共计 8*2&#x3D;16</li><li>分区 20230501 to 20230502，每个分区有1个删除操作，共计 2*1&#x3D;2</li></ul></li><li>2个新增操作清单：<ul><li>分区 20230501 to 20230502，每个分区有1个新增操作，共计 2*1&#x3D;2</li></ul></li></ul>          </div><h5 id="修改表信息"><a href="#修改表信息" class="headerlink" title="修改表信息"></a>修改表信息</h5><p>表的修改通常是元数据信息的修改，也即 <code>schema</code> 文件夹的变动，当我们执行以下SQL时：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">ALTER</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">SET</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;full-compaction.delta-commits&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会在 schema 文件夹下新增一个 <code>schema-1</code> 文件，内容描述了新的表配置信息(元数据增量状态)</p><h5 id="快照过期"><a href="#快照过期" class="headerlink" title="快照过期"></a>快照过期</h5><p>无论如何在SQL语义的层面增删数据，只要快照还未过期，都不会导致数据的真正删除。因为 Paimon 提供了时间旅行的功能用于回溯早期的快照版本。</p><p>具体和快照过期相关的参数如下：</p><ul><li><strong>snapshot.time-retained</strong>：快照的保留时间（默认1hour）</li><li><strong>snapshot.num-retained.min</strong>：快照数目的阈值下限（默认10个）<span class="label label-success">≥</span></li><li><strong>snapshot.num-retained.max</strong>：快照数目的阈值上限（默认Integer.MAX_VALUE）<span class="label label-success">≤</span></li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>当快照数目小于 <code>snapshot.num-retained.min</code> 时，没有快照会被过期（即使达到了 <code>snapshot.time-retained</code>）<br>当快照数目唱过 <code>snapshot.num-retained.min</code> 后，按照 <code>snapshot.time-retained</code> 和 <code>snapshot.num-retained.max</code> 来控制过期策略。</p>          </div><p><img src="/img/paimon-file-operations-4.png" alt="过期流程"></p><p>当然，如果想要回滚某个已经被删除的快照版本，Paimon 也提供了工具：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;FLINK_HOME&#125;</span><br>./bin/flink run \<br>    /path/to/paimon-flink-action-0.5-SNAPSHOT.jar \<br>    rollback-to \<br>    --warehouse &lt;warehouse-path&gt; \<br>    --database &lt;database-name&gt; \ <br>    --table &lt;table-name&gt; \<br>    --snapshot &lt;snapshot-id&gt; \<br>    [--catalog-conf &lt;paimon-catalog-conf&gt; [--catalog-conf &lt;paimon-catalog-conf&gt; ...]]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="Flink流写操作"><a href="#Flink流写操作" class="headerlink" title="Flink流写操作"></a>Flink流写操作</h5><p>请跳转 &#x3D;&gt; <a href="http://#">Paimon-[番外]-FlinkCDC案例</a> 😼</p><h3 id="1-5-主键表"><a href="#1-5-主键表" class="headerlink" title="1.5 主键表"></a>1.5 主键表</h3><p><code>Changelog表</code> 是创建表时的<strong>默认表类型</strong>。用户可以在表中插入、更新或删除记录。<br>主键是每条记录唯一的一组列。Paimon会强制排序数据，这意味着在每个bucket中，数据是被排列好的，因此用户可以通过<u>在主键上添加过滤条件来实现高性能</u>。</p><h4 id="1-5-1-合并引擎"><a href="#1-5-1-合并引擎" class="headerlink" title="1.5.1 合并引擎"></a>1.5.1 合并引擎</h4><p><code>Paimon Sink</code> 接收到上游一批数据且其中包含重复组件数据时，会对那部分数据进行合并<sup>merge</sup>，以确保数据的唯一，用户可以通过指定 <span class="label label-info">merge-engine</span> 参数来定义合并策略。</p><ul><li><strong>去重合并引擎</strong><sup>deduplicate</sup><span class="label label-default">默认</span>：将最近接触到的数据(全字段)替换之前的旧数据；</li><li><strong>部分更新引擎</strong><sup>partial-update</sup>：将最近接触到的数据(部分字段)替换之前的旧数据；<blockquote><p>可以看做是除了主键外的字段全按照 <code>COALESCE(column, null)</code> 处理</p></blockquote></li><li><strong>聚集合并引擎</strong><sup>aggregation</sup>：按提供的聚合函数规则，将最近接触到的数据(部分字段)替换之前的旧数据。<blockquote><p>目前支持 <code>sum</code>、<code>min/max</code>、<code>last_value/last_non_null_value</code>、<code>listagg</code>、<code>bool_and/bool_or</code><br>并且当前仅有 <code>sum</code> 原生支持 回撤<sup>retraction</sup>，其他四个函数必须通过设置 <code>&#39;fields.$&#123;field_name&#125;.ignore-retract&#39;=&#39;true&#39;</code> 从而支持回撤。</p></blockquote></li><li><strong>首行合并引擎</strong><sup>first-row</sup>：保持首个数据。</li></ul><div class="note note-info">            <p>流式查询时，<code>partial-update</code>引擎 &amp; <code>first-row</code>引擎 必须和 <code>lookup</code>型 <strong>OR</strong> <code>full-compaction</code>型 的 Changelog 制造器一起使用！</p>          </div><div class="note note-info">            <p><code>partial-update</code>引擎无法接受<em>DELETE操作</em>的信息，因为该行为无法被定义。用户可以通过配置 <code>partial-update.ignore-delete=DELETE</code>来忽略<em>DELETE操作</em></p>          </div><div class="note note-info">            <p><code>first-row</code>引擎仅支持插入顺序，所以无法为其指定 <code>squence.field</code> 参数，此外它也不接受 <em>DELETE操作</em> 和 <em>UPDATE_BEFORE操作</em></p>          </div><div class="note note-warning">            <p>在 FlinkSQL 中设置 <code>table.exec.sink.upsert-materialize=NONE</code> 总是会导致奇怪的行为，所以当明确摄入的数据是乱序的时候，请阅读并使用 <a href="#153">序列化字段</a></p>          </div><h4 id="1-5-2-Changelog-制造器"><a href="#1-5-2-Changelog-制造器" class="headerlink" title="1.5.2 Changelog 制造器"></a>1.5.2 Changelog 制造器</h4><p>流式查询会不断生产出变更<sup>changes</sup>，我们可以通过指定 &#96;&#96; 这个表属性来进行制造器的切换。</p><ul><li><strong>None</strong><sup>无</sup>：仅看得到合并后的数据结果，无法回溯旧的数据状态；<span class="label label-danger">不建议</span></li><li><strong>Input</strong><sup>(常规)输入型</sup>：将输入的记录直接刷写到独立的changelog文件中。<span class="label label-success">建议</span></li><li><strong>Lookup</strong><sup>检索型</sup>：使用缓存辅助changelog的刷写。<span class="label label-warning">试验</span></li><li><strong>Full Compaction</strong><sup>全压缩</sup>：对于读延迟过高的场景可以使用该制造器，它分离了 <code>数据刷写</code> 和 <code>日志生成</code> 两个流程，加速查询，但是写延迟升高。<span class="label label-danger">不建议</span></li></ul><h4 id="1-5-3-序列字段"><a href="#1-5-3-序列字段" class="headerlink" title="1.5.3 序列字段"></a><span id="153">1.5.3 序列字段</span></h4><p>正常情况下，主键表都是按照数据输入顺序进行合并的，当数据是乱序的情况下，会导致合并结果不正确。对比Flink水印的概念，我们在Paimon的主键表中指定一个时间类型字段 <code>sequence.field</code> 来纠正乱序问题。例如在 FlinkSQL 建表语句中：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> MyTable (<br>    pk <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY <span class="hljs-keyword">NOT</span> ENFORCED,<br>    v1 <span class="hljs-keyword">DOUBLE</span>,<br>    v2 <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span>,<br>    dt <span class="hljs-type">TIMESTAMP</span><br>) <span class="hljs-keyword">WITH</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;sequence.field&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dt&#x27;</span><br>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-5-4-序列组"><a href="#1-5-4-序列组" class="headerlink" title="1.5.4 序列组"></a>1.5.4 序列组</h4><p>当合并引擎是 <code>partial-update</code> 引擎且接受多流输入时，光靠 <code>sequence-field</code> 可能无法解决乱序问题，因为在<strong>流A</strong>上的 <code>sequence-field</code> 可能会被<strong>流B</strong>上的更新操作覆盖。</p><p><strong>案例</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> T (<br>    k <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    a <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    b <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    g_1 <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    c <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    d <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    g_2 <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">PRIMARY</span> KEY (k) <span class="hljs-keyword">NOT</span> ENFORCED<br>) <span class="hljs-keyword">WITH</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;merge-engine&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;partial-update&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fields.g_1.sequence-group&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a,b&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;fields.g_2.sequence-group&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-operator">=</span><span class="hljs-string">&#x27;c,d&#x27;</span><br>);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">-- g_2 is null, c, d should not be updated</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">CAST</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">NULL</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">AS</span> <span class="hljs-type">INT</span>));<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> T; <span class="hljs-comment">-- output 1, 2, 2, 2, 1, 1, 1</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">-- g_1 is smaller, a, b should not be updated</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">INSERT</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">INTO</span> T <span class="hljs-keyword">VALUES</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="hljs-operator">*</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">FROM</span> T; <span class="hljs-comment">-- output 1, 2, 2, 2, 3, 3, 3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-6-仅追加表"><a href="#1-6-仅追加表" class="headerlink" title="1.6 仅追加表"></a>1.6 仅追加表</h3><p>日志数据的同步往往不关心数据的更新，纯增量数据转换而来的表，无需定义主键的概念。</p><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">CREATE</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">TABLE</span> MyTable (<br>    product_id <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span>,<br>    price <span class="hljs-keyword">DOUBLE</span>,<br>    sales <span class="hljs-type">BIGINT</span><br>) <span class="hljs-keyword">WITH</span> (<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;bucket&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;8&#x27;</span>,<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;bucket-key&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;product_id&#x27;</span><br>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note note-info">            <p>但我们建议设置 <code>bucket-key</code> 属性，否则每行数据将会被散列化，导致性能下降</p>          </div><h4 id="1-6-1-压缩策略"><a href="#1-6-1-压缩策略" class="headerlink" title="1.6.1 压缩策略"></a>1.6.1 压缩策略</h4><p>可以控制压缩策略的配置：</p><ul><li><strong>write-only</strong>：<span class="label label-default">default:false</span> 只写模式下不跳过 <code>数据压缩</code> 和 <code>快照过期</code> 流程；</li><li><strong>compaction.min.file-num</strong>：<span class="label label-default">default:5</span> 数据文件压缩触发阈值下限。</li><li><strong>compaction.max.file-num</strong>：<span class="label label-default">default:50</span> 数据文件压缩触发阈值上限。</li></ul><h3 id="1-7-外部日志系统"><a href="#1-7-外部日志系统" class="headerlink" title="1.7 外部日志系统"></a>1.7 外部日志系统</h3><p>主要是接入 <code>Kafka</code> 等日志系统。具体可参考 <a href="https://paimon.apache.org/docs/master/concepts/external-log-systems/#supported-log-systems">最新官网文档说明</a></p>]]></content